des:
This skill will quiz you on many different movies, do you think that you can get them all correct? Alexa will ask you 5 questions at a time, try to get them all right. There is also a surprise waiting for you when you get all the questions correct or wrong! 

Try it out and see if you can beat Alexa!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
